35
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:44,280
Each search engine uses its own algorithm to rank the pages based on what it thinks you want.

36
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:50,480
The search engine's ranking algorithm might check if
your search term shows up in the page title,

37
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:55,790
it might check if all of the words
show up next to each other, or any number

