47
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:40,840
Search engines
regularly update their algorithms to

48
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:44,480
prevent fake or untrustworthy sites from
reaching the top.

49
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:50,120
Ultimately, it's up to you to keep an eye out for these
pages that are untrustworthy by looking

50
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:53,340
at the web address and making sure it's
a reliable source.

51
