for "large pitcher" it will find you options for you kitchen.

59
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:43,380
To understand the words better, we use something called machine learning, a type of artificial intelligence.

60
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:47,340
It enables search algorithms
to search not just individual letters or

61
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:51,800
words in the page, but understand the
underlying meaning of the words.

